<plot>Join ranger Liesl Eichenberg and renowned wildlife photographer Tim Liversedge, on a live-action 3D IMAX photo-safari on the waterways of the Okavango Delta in Botswana. Come face-to-face with some of the most majestic animals inhabiting this corner of paradise, including lions, elephants, crocodiles, hippos and the Pels fishing owls.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?024838</url></doc>
